WEBVTT

00:00:27.163 --> 00:00:32.506
JANUARY TWELFTH NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN. SURVIVIR Yisroel Pinksovitsh.

00:00:32.665 --> 00:00:38.734
INTERVIEWER ROBERT JACOB KURTZMAN. BAT YAM, ISRAEL. LANGUAGE OF INTERVIEW, YIDDISH.

00:00:41.946 --> 00:00:49.905
SHMI ROBERT YAKOV KURTZMAN. HAYOM YOM RISHON, YANUAR SHTEYM ESREY, ELEF TSHA MEOT TISHIM VESEHVA.

00:00:50.451 --> 00:00:57.111
ANI ORECH RAYON IM YISRAEL Pinksovitsh, BEBAT YAM, YISRAEL.

00:01:01.335 --> 00:01:02.814
vos iz ayer nomen?

00:01:02.955 --> 00:01:05.412
Yisrael Pinkasovitsh.

00:01:07.309 --> 00:01:09.024
un ayer geburtstog?

00:01:09.182 --> 00:01:13.732
dem tsveytn yener toyznt naynt hundert akht un tsvontsik.

00:01:13.873 --> 00:01:15.858
vi alt zent ir yetst?

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:19.891
nayn un fertsik yor. nayn un zekhtsik yor.

00:01:18.750 --> 00:01:20.043
nayn un zekhtsik.

00:01:21.568 --> 00:01:23.553
velkhe vu zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:24.049 --> 00:01:25.528
Negrovits.

00:01:25.618 --> 00:01:27.243
Negrovits.

00:01:26.243 --> 00:01:27.620
Negrovits.

00:01:27.243 --> 00:01:30.742
N.A.G.R.O. v- W.I.C.

00:01:30.934 --> 00:01:32.295
vu iz dos?

00:01:32.655 --> 00:01:34.640
in Karpatruserland.

00:01:34.478 --> 00:01:39.011
Karpat-Rusland. ven ir zent geboyrn iz dos geven CZECHOSLOVAKIA.

00:01:37.836 --> 00:01:39.382
Tshekhoslovakay.

00:01:40.755 --> 00:01:42.588
vos iz der tatn's nomen?

00:01:42.848 --> 00:01:45.289
Leyb Pinkasovitsh.

00:01:45.717 --> 00:01:47.196
Arye Leyb?

00:01:46.678 --> 00:01:48.899
Arye Leyb Pinkasovitsh.

00:01:47.758 --> 00:01:49.051
Pinkasovitsh.

00:01:49.564 --> 00:01:52.325
un vu iz er geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:52.112 --> 00:01:53.523
in Negrovits.

00:01:53.142 --> 00:01:54.435
Negrovits.

00:01:56.449 --> 00:01:58.990
di muter's nomen?

00:01:59.115 --> 00:02:02.012
Yakobovitsh Gitl.

00:02:02.035 --> 00:02:03.244
Gitl.

00:02:03.469 --> 00:02:05.454
un vu iz zi geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:05.258 --> 00:02:06.517
Voshana.

00:02:06.726 --> 00:02:08.306
Voshana.

00:02:07.907 --> 00:02:08.795
yo.

00:02:10.151 --> 00:02:15.017
W.O.S.H.A.N.A.

00:02:15.017 --> 00:02:16.980
vu iz dos? oykhet in,

00:02:16.935 --> 00:02:20.321
oykh in Karpat-Rusland. nisht vayt fun Negrovits.

00:02:19.365 --> 00:02:26.058
aha, ober ven zi iz geboyrn dos iz geven AUSTRO-HUNGARY.

00:02:25.086 --> 00:02:26.210
Ungariye.

00:02:26.115 --> 00:02:27.999
un der tatn oykhet.

00:02:27.263 --> 00:02:28.818
oykh Oystro-Ungarn.

00:02:30.537 --> 00:02:32.606
vos iz geven der tatn's fakh?

00:02:34.620 --> 00:02:41.094
der tate, m'hot gehat feld, gevezn beheymes,

00:02:41.117 --> 00:02:46.767
un der tate hot zikh nokh farnumen mit nor

00:02:46.767 --> 00:02:51.320
alt vos iz gegangen oyf iberarbetn fetns un azolkhe zakhn.

00:02:52.778 --> 00:02:58.897
a mol hot men tsamgenumen alte zakhn, skhoyres, un m'hot dos geshikt in der fabrik.

00:02:56.018 --> 00:02:56.923
yo?

00:02:58.633 --> 00:03:01.968
a, metalishe zakhn, yo, a.

00:03:00.540 --> 00:03:01.377
yo.

00:03:03.072 --> 00:03:06.070
az er hot geha- er iz geven a lands-arbayter?

00:03:06.008 --> 00:03:06.778
yo.

00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:09.228
ir hot gehat hin?

00:03:09.113 --> 00:03:10.221
ales.

00:03:09.228 --> 00:03:14.467
un un un un un he- un milkh koy- ki?

00:03:10.429 --> 00:03:11.351
ki.

00:03:13.534 --> 00:03:14.456
yo.

00:03:14.467 --> 00:03:17.916
un a YERAKOT oykhet?

00:03:17.061 --> 00:03:18.152
ales.

00:03:18.883 --> 00:03:21.796
er vet es farkoyfn, tsi oder s'do,

00:03:20.908 --> 00:03:23.349
NO, meyn oyf eygn gebroykh.

00:03:23.119 --> 00:03:24.260
far eygn gebroykh.

00:03:24.030 --> 00:03:24.749
yo.

00:03:24.452 --> 00:03:31.823
ober di gesheft iz geven mit di mit di alte zakhn vos er hot gekoyft un er flegt es farkoyfn tsu a fabrik?

00:03:28.435 --> 00:03:29.340
yo.

00:03:31.675 --> 00:03:32.614
yo.

00:03:31.823 --> 00:03:33.170
aha.

00:03:35.708 --> 00:03:38.553
vifl kinder zenen ir geven in shtub?

00:03:39.201 --> 00:03:40.595
finef brider.

00:03:40.365 --> 00:03:43.768
finef nor brider. un ir zent?

00:03:45.647 --> 00:03:47.480
ikh bin farn klenstn.

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:49.454
farn klenstn.

00:03:48.448 --> 00:03:49.758
farn klenstn.

00:03:49.528 --> 00:03:50.517
aha.

00:03:51.283 --> 00:03:56.897
ir zent di ferter. ferter zun, yo yo.

00:03:55.435 --> 00:03:56.289
yo.

00:04:06.252 --> 00:04:10.582
vu vu hot ir gelernt? velkhe shule?

00:04:10.808 --> 00:04:18.530
bayn undz iz gevezn far bay di tshekhn, di yidn zenen gegangen in a tshekhisher shul,

00:04:18.942 --> 00:04:22.052
un goyim zenen gegangen in an ukrainisher shul.

00:04:21.962 --> 00:04:22.698
aha.

00:04:22.052 --> 00:04:25.112
ikh hob gelernt in a tshekhisher shul a halbn tog,

00:04:25.152 --> 00:04:29.196
un a halbn tog hob ikh gelernt in a kheyder, in a yidishn kheyder.

00:04:29.218 --> 00:04:32.249
aha, nokh mitog?

00:04:32.779 --> 00:04:36.080
a mol iz geven far mitog, a mol nokh mitog. ven UNK.

00:04:36.137 --> 00:04:44.450
di shtot vu ir zent geboyrn gevorn, Nagrovitsh, hot an anderer nomen oykhet, yo?

00:04:43.596 --> 00:04:47.404
bay di ungern hot zi geheysn FELSOKALOCSA.

00:04:47.427 --> 00:04:55.403
FELSOKALOCSA. F.E.L.S.O. UMLAUT K.O.L.O.C.S.A.

00:04:55.493 --> 00:04:57.630
ober bay haynt,

00:04:58.193 --> 00:04:59.385
Negrovits.

00:04:58.243 --> 00:05:00.616
neyn, Negrovitsh.

00:05:05.230 --> 00:05:09.661
az ir hot gelernt in der fri in dem shtat-shule.

00:05:10.123 --> 00:05:12.260
demolts nokh mitog in kheyder.

00:05:11.541 --> 00:05:13.284
ye in in kheyder.

00:05:13.284 --> 00:05:19.179
in kheyder iz s'geven eyn klas far ale kinder, or s-

00:05:19.287 --> 00:05:22.042
ikh kon dos nisht zogn vi azoy s'gevezn.

00:05:22.042 --> 00:05:30.640
vayl koydem iz geven an alte shul, hot men gelernt in der alter shul. un dernokh dem, yede vokh, hot men bay

00:05:24.771 --> 00:05:25.507
yo.

00:05:30.640 --> 00:05:33.658
eyn vokh alts bayn a TALMID in der heym gelernt.

00:05:35.470 --> 00:05:39.649
ah Negrovitsh, dos iz geven a dorf?

00:05:38.625 --> 00:05:39.699
a dorf.

00:05:39.925 --> 00:05:43.682
a a sakh yidn, oder di maystns zenen geven goyim?

00:05:42.726 --> 00:05:49.976
NO. in tsenter, in MERKAZ, hobn gevoynt nayn un nayntsik protsent nor yidn.

00:05:50.117 --> 00:05:54.566
s'geven beerekh a fertsik fuftsik mishpokhes hobn gevoynt.

00:05:56.884 --> 00:06:06.432
un vi, s'nisht di shtub, ir hot gehat a a a hoyz,

00:06:06.432 --> 00:06:09.855
di nekste hoyz, dos iz geven goyim, dos iz geven yidn?

00:06:09.726 --> 00:06:14.259
NO. bayn undz iz geven fun beyde zaytn iz gevezn yidn.

00:06:13.843 --> 00:06:14.900
fun yidn?

00:06:14.451 --> 00:06:15.373
yo.

00:06:14.957 --> 00:06:15.862
aha.

00:06:16.813 --> 00:06:20.654
vos hobn zey getun? zenen oykhet geven fakhman?

00:06:21.775 --> 00:06:28.468
m'hot gehat feld, m'hot gehat ferd. a mol hot men gefirt skhoyres

00:06:28.710 --> 00:06:32.450
in di geshefter, nisht mit oytos, mit ferd hot men gefirt.

00:06:37.958 --> 00:06:47.317
az di milkhome iz gekumen tsu aykh in eyn un fertsik, far dem iz geven epes

00:06:47.543 --> 00:06:53.443
ven hot men hot ongehoybn mit mit mit mit mitn gelbn mogn-dovid?

00:06:52.673 --> 00:06:57.459
far mir hot men ongehongen in dray un fertsiker yor.

00:06:58.326 --> 00:06:59.841
ikh vel aykh bald zogn far,

00:06:58.343 --> 00:07:01.982
a dray un a. dos iz shpeter. yo yo yo.

00:06:59.841 --> 00:07:01.644
ikh vel aykh bald zogn far vos.

00:07:02.275 --> 00:07:06.824
far dem, in eyn un fertsiker yor, in yuli,

00:07:06.628 --> 00:07:07.533
yuli,

00:07:07.557 --> 00:07:11.044
hot men tsamgenumen ale yidn funem dorf in a shule,

00:07:11.927 --> 00:07:15.358
un dernokh dem hot men, in a shule, yo.

00:07:13.108 --> 00:07:14.266
in a shule?

00:07:15.358 --> 00:07:17.068
un dernokh dem hot men,

00:07:17.226 --> 00:07:20.749
dos tate, muters, ale?

00:07:19.048 --> 00:07:21.101
ales, di ale mishpokhes.

00:07:20.749 --> 00:07:21.725
yungers?

00:07:21.394 --> 00:07:25.947
un nokh dem iz men gegangen, m'hot oysgeveylt akht mishpokhes fun undz,

00:07:25.947 --> 00:07:28.155
un m'hot oyfgezetst oyf MASAITn,

00:07:27.958 --> 00:07:33.976
dos iz geven akht mishpokhes fun vifl? nor fun, dos iz geven a halbe dorf?

00:07:29.832 --> 00:07:33.369
funem dorf. funem dorf, fun undzer dorf,

00:07:34.084 --> 00:07:36.812
NO s'geven veyniker vi a halb, veynik.

00:07:35.603 --> 00:07:36.322
aha.

00:07:36.936 --> 00:07:39.326
di iberike hot men gelozt aheym,

00:07:39.568 --> 00:07:43.851
un undz hot men farlodnt oyf MASAITn, oyf last-oytos,

00:07:43.851 --> 00:07:47.882
un m'hot avekgefirt oyf Khust, oyf oyf der ban,

00:07:48.175 --> 00:07:54.548
un dort hot men farlodnt in vagonen in der ban, fun der gantser gegnt iz geven a gantser ban,

00:07:54.925 --> 00:07:59.171
un m'hot undz avekgefirt biz keyn Rakhev oyf der grenets,

00:07:59.599 --> 00:08:02.310
un dort hot men tsurik oyf gelodnt

00:08:02.113 --> 00:08:04.857
vu vu vu oyfn baym grenets?

00:08:05.033 --> 00:08:06.782
Rakhov, Yasin.

00:08:07.024 --> 00:08:08.368
Yasin.

00:08:07.733 --> 00:08:08.841
Yasin.

00:08:09.994 --> 00:08:11.338
Yasin, dos iz,

00:08:12.002 --> 00:08:13.093
dos a,

00:08:12.053 --> 00:08:14.848
d- dos iz a grenets mit Rumanye?

00:08:14.331 --> 00:08:18.105
NO, deys iz a grenets mit Poyln gevezn, mit Poyln.

00:08:16.542 --> 00:08:21.179
mit Poyln. Yasin.

00:08:20.170 --> 00:08:21.261
Yasin.

00:08:21.179 --> 00:08:23.659
J.A.S.S.I.N.

00:08:23.659 --> 00:08:24.399
yo?

00:08:24.878 --> 00:08:30.002
dort hot men undz oyfgelodnt oyf MASAITn, un m'hot aribergefirt der grenets

00:08:31.577 --> 00:08:35.269
ven it zolt der, ver ver iz ver hot aykh gefirt di zhandem-

00:08:32.235 --> 00:08:33.005
oyf Poyl-

00:08:34.142 --> 00:08:35.435
di ungarn.

00:08:35.269 --> 00:08:37.257
ungarn? zhandermey?

00:08:35.678 --> 00:08:37.612
di ungarn, di zhondarmerye.

00:08:38.023 --> 00:08:45.560
m'hot undz aribergefirt di grenets, oyf der poylisher zayt, dort zenen geven di daytshn.

00:08:46.495 --> 00:08:51.841
m'hot undz zofort tsurik farlodnt, nokh a mol in vagonen, in RAKEVET,

00:08:51.841 --> 00:08:55.180
azolkhe ofene vagonen vos m'hot gefirt nor holts,

00:08:56.333 --> 00:08:59.668
un dort hobn di daytshn, zofort, ven undz ze'mir gekumen ahin,

00:08:59.910 --> 00:09:07.414
ze'mir gevezn, eltere mentshn zenen geven in bord un peyes, yinglekh ze'mir ale geven, ikh hob oykh getrogn peyes.

00:09:07.453 --> 00:09:13.606
di daytshn hobn ongehoybn tsu flikn far mentshn di bord, mit di peyes, un m'hot geharget un m'hot geshlogn,

00:09:14.052 --> 00:09:16.374
un m'hot undz farlodnt oyf di vagonen,

00:09:16.549 --> 00:09:22.398
un mir ze'mir geforn ikh veys nisht vu biz vu, un biz Kolomoy.

00:09:22.337 --> 00:09:24.435
ir zent tsvelef yor alt geven demolts?

00:09:24.312 --> 00:09:25.656
draytsn yor.

00:09:24.435 --> 00:09:26.634
a a.

00:09:26.067 --> 00:09:27.529
draytsn yor.

00:09:27.737 --> 00:09:29.098
in Kolomoy,

00:09:29.290 --> 00:09:30.645
hot men undz tsurik

00:09:29.762 --> 00:09:31.156
Kolomoy.

00:09:30.645 --> 00:09:31.899
Kolomoy.

00:09:31.348 --> 00:09:34.771
K.O.L.O.M.O.I.

00:09:34.771 --> 00:09:35.983
vu iz dos?

00:09:36.124 --> 00:09:39.546
deys iz Galitsye iz dos gevezn.

00:09:37.963 --> 00:09:39.560
Galitsye.

00:09:39.546 --> 00:09:41.484
demolts hot men es ongerufn Poyln.

00:09:41.389 --> 00:09:43.391
Poyln Galitsye, ye.

00:09:41.980 --> 00:09:43.425
Poyln hot, yo.

00:09:43.482 --> 00:09:45.686
dos iz geven a groyse shtetl, yo?

00:09:45.591 --> 00:09:49.719
yo. ikh bin nor, lebn shtetl ze'mir durkhgegangen.

00:09:49.472 --> 00:09:50.394
aha.

00:09:50.485 --> 00:09:54.951
m'hot undz farlodnt tsurik oyf MASAITn, di ungarishe soldatn,

00:09:55.159 --> 00:09:58.258
un m'hot undz aribergefirt dem Dnyester, a taykh,

00:09:58.112 --> 00:09:59.304
Dnyester.

00:09:58.922 --> 00:10:00.097
Dnyester.

00:10:00.070 --> 00:10:03.270
D.N.I.E.S.T.E.R.

00:10:03.411 --> 00:10:05.177
a shtetele Klust.

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:06.274
Klust?

00:10:05.976 --> 00:10:06.830
yo.

00:10:07.461 --> 00:10:10.155
K.L.U.S.T.

00:10:08.963 --> 00:10:10.256
Klust.

00:10:11.038 --> 00:10:16.719
dort hot men undz gezogt m'zol mir geyn foroys un nisht umkern zikh tsurik.

00:10:17.012 --> 00:10:18.862
ir blaybt dortn in Klust?

00:10:18.379 --> 00:10:22.558
in Klust az mir zol'mir geyn tsu fus, alts foroys, nisht zayn dortn.

00:10:23.425 --> 00:10:24.566
tsu vanen?

00:10:26.007 --> 00:10:31.603
m'hot gezogt az m'hot gehert keile m'vil mir zol'mir tsu di rusn aribergeyn.

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:41.087
der emes iz gevezn az m'iz dergangen biz in Kaminits-Padolsk, ver s'iz dergangen, dort hot men oysgeshosn.

00:10:41.110 --> 00:10:42.977
Kamenits-Padolsk?

00:10:41.970 --> 00:10:43.030
Podolsk.

00:10:43.030 --> 00:10:48.293
dort hot men oys geshisn. undz ze'mir dergangen gegangen, ikh veys nisht vifl BEDIYUK,

00:10:48.298 --> 00:10:53.152
a tog tsvey, ober vifl, ze'mir ongekumen tsun a shtetele,

00:10:53.310 --> 00:10:59.835
s'hot geheysn vi azoy ikh hob fargesn. Bo- s'hot geheysn Borshtshava.

00:10:57.327 --> 00:10:58.401
m'geyt tsu fus?

00:10:59.875 --> 00:11:01.826
Boshtshava?

00:11:00.027 --> 00:11:01.911
Borshtshava.

00:11:03.132 --> 00:11:07.209
dort ze'mir arayn in shtot, un mir ze'mir,

00:11:06.017 --> 00:11:10.263
Borshtshava. B.O.S.H.

00:11:07.688 --> 00:11:08.559
yo,

00:11:11.181 --> 00:11:12.727
A.V.A.

00:11:13.442 --> 00:11:15.663
dos iz a shtetl, dos iz?

00:11:14.455 --> 00:11:15.748
a shtetl.

00:11:16.193 --> 00:11:18.988
dos iz shoyn geven tsvishn tog un nakht.

00:11:21.036 --> 00:11:26.514
nor ze'mir vi s'kumt a yid mit a langer bord, un geyt mit der MADRICHA

00:11:26.537 --> 00:11:31.120
in der zayt, un shrayt oyf undz, "raboysim, nokh mir!"

00:11:32.713 --> 00:11:35.525
azoy ze'mir gegangen, un der linker,

00:11:34.468 --> 00:11:36.183
ver iz der yid geven?

00:11:36.021 --> 00:11:39.207
ikh hob nisht a an aynvoyner fun dem shtetl.

00:11:39.207 --> 00:11:45.076
vayl di yidn hot men nokh nisht genumen fun der heym. zey zenen nokh geven in der heym, di yidn fun dem shtetl.

00:11:45.859 --> 00:11:48.522
er hot undz arayngefirt oyf links in a gas,

00:11:48.522 --> 00:11:53.610
dort in a BET-KNESET, in a shul, un dort hot men undz bahaltn.

00:11:53.132 --> 00:11:54.307
bahaltn?

00:11:53.610 --> 00:11:54.628
yo.

00:11:55.832 --> 00:11:59.201
un er hot dort, er hot mit dertseylt nokh zakhn tsu aykh?

00:11:59.916 --> 00:12:03.352
vos tsu tsu tsu yidn in in Kamenits-Padolsk?

00:12:03.645 --> 00:12:11.337
m'hot nokh dem hot men ho'mir ongehoybn tsu hern az dort ver s'dergeyt ahin, harget men oys.

00:12:11.337 --> 00:12:13.174
vegn dem hot men undz bahaltn.

00:12:13.905 --> 00:12:17.847
di eltern, elter mentshn zenen fun dort keyn mol nisht aroysgegangen,

00:12:17.854 --> 00:12:23.133
un undz kinder ze'mir shoyn geven on peyes, m'hot nisht gevust tsi undz ze'mir yidn ober kristn,

00:12:23.133 --> 00:12:26.769
flegn mir aroysgeyn, mir fleg avekgeyn in dem SHUK,

00:12:26.769 --> 00:12:29.629
vos m'hot aroysgevorfn un genumen tsu esn.

00:12:29.629 --> 00:12:34.402
un azoy ze'mir undz dort geven a gantsn zumer, biz far rosheshone.

00:12:35.235 --> 00:12:37.442
dos iz Bosh-

00:12:36.568 --> 00:12:37.979
in Boshtshava.

00:12:37.442 --> 00:12:40.261
Boshtshava. biz far rosheshone?

00:12:39.387 --> 00:12:40.697
far rosheshone.

00:12:40.261 --> 00:12:45.256
far rosheshone, in eyn un fertsik.

00:12:44.162 --> 00:12:45.607
in eyn un fertsik.

00:12:45.256 --> 00:12:46.822
eyn un fertsik, yo.

00:12:46.690 --> 00:12:50.242
far rosheshone, ho'mir zikh genumen tsurikgeyn,

00:12:50.242 --> 00:12:54.317
iz dortn, der yid mit der langer bord, un nokh a reb eyner,

00:12:54.317 --> 00:12:58.351
