00:25:15.657 --> 00:25:22.226
mit dem iz mir geblibn in zikorn, azoy oyf links iz geshtanen a daytsh un er hot gehalt a sider in di hent,

00:25:22.226 --> 00:25:27.480
un er hot zikh gemakht a TZKHOK, er hot zikh ongehoybn tsu betn keile er hot gedavnt.

00:25:28.161 --> 00:25:29.842
a daytshisher soldat?

00:25:28.667 --> 00:25:32.880
a daytshisher soldat. er hot a sider genumen un er hot zikh gemakht keilu er hot gedavnt.

00:25:33.696 --> 00:25:36.660
azoy hot men undz avekgefirt, mir ze'mir gekumen,

00:25:35.670 --> 00:25:38.718
az der tatn iz nisht geven mit aykh.

00:25:38.320 --> 00:25:42.296
NO, oyf links avek. ikh hob nisht gevust nokh demolts vu m'firt.

00:25:43.332 --> 00:25:46.324
azoy hot men undz gebrengt in aza groysn gebay,

00:25:46.324 --> 00:25:49.218
keile m'hot gemeynt az mir gey'mir zikh dortn bodn.

00:25:49.218 --> 00:25:55.807
dort hot men oysgetun ale kleyder vos m'hot gehat. eyn zakh vos m'hot gemegt aribertrogn, di shikh.

00:25:54.976 --> 00:25:56.408
di shikh, yo.

00:25:55.807 --> 00:26:03.677
di shikh. dort hot men opgeshorn umetum di hor, un m'iz durkh, m'hot bakukt ales,

00:26:04.071 --> 00:26:07.878
un di shikh hot men azoy mit di he- hent aroyfgegangen,

00:26:08.458 --> 00:26:13.902
un dort hot men undz gegebn kleyder, azelkhe kleyder hot men gegebn vi pizhames,

00:26:14.280 --> 00:26:18.746
geshtrayfte kleyder, hot men gegebn a hoyz, a hemd,

00:26:18.769 --> 00:26:25.732
un aza lang aza vi a rekl, a langs, un a hitl. deys zenen geven di gantse kleyder.

00:26:26.228 --> 00:26:29.242
fun dort hot men undz avekgefirt in a blok,

00:26:30.025 --> 00:26:32.364
dos iz geven in Aushvits in Birkenou,

00:26:33.028 --> 00:26:35.536
ir zent geven in Birkenau?

00:26:35.121 --> 00:26:37.039
in Birkenau. yo.

00:26:36.302 --> 00:26:37.899
s'iz s'iz glaykh, s'iz,

00:26:37.332 --> 00:26:38.321
yo.

00:26:39.137 --> 00:26:45.341
un dort ze'mir gevezn, ober oyfn tsveytn ober oyfn dritn tog hot men undz genumen

00:26:45.516 --> 00:26:49.593
undzer blok un m'hot farlodnt in a ban, in a RAKEVET,

00:26:50.410 --> 00:26:57.559
un m'hot undz gezogt az m'firt undz lernen fakhn, MIKTZOAs az m'lernt undz, firt un lernen.

00:26:57.868 --> 00:27:01.034
s'ales geven yunge kinder. m'hot arayngezetst in va-

00:27:00.214 --> 00:27:01.980
ir zent geven mit di brider?

00:27:01.986 --> 00:27:04.899
n- ikh mit eyn bruder, mit mit Avromen.

00:27:03.420 --> 00:27:05.405
n- nor mit Avrom.

00:27:06.137 --> 00:27:09.219
yener bruder Moyshe iz geven in an andern blok.

00:27:13.461 --> 00:27:16.824
un m'hot undz farlodnt in vagon.

00:27:16.824 --> 00:27:23.985
azoy eyner farn andern iz gezesn tsvishn di fis. azoy hot men farlodnt. in der mit iz geshtanen tsvey S.S.layt.

00:27:25.088 --> 00:27:29.233
vi m'hot undz gegebn dort tsu shtikele broyt un m'hot undz farlodnt in vagon,

00:27:29.475 --> 00:27:32.101
vifl tsayt s'hot genumen, veys ikh nisht,

00:27:32.209 --> 00:27:36.540
mir ze'mir ongekumen keyn Bukhnvald. ze'mir ongekumen bay nakht,

00:27:34.116 --> 00:27:35.257
Bukhnvald.

00:27:37.204 --> 00:27:43.678
bay nakht hot men geheysn, m'hot undz arayngefirt oykhet in aza groys gebay, mir ho'mir gemeynt az s'iz tsu bodn,

00:27:43.701 --> 00:27:48.200
yedes hot oysgetun di kleyder, naket iz men dort geshtanen a gantse nakht.

00:27:48.628 --> 00:27:55.035
s'geven azoy fil mentshn vos az emetser hot zikh aropgezetst hot er shoyn nisht gekont oyfshteyn.

00:27:56.087 --> 00:27:58.511
dos iz geven in velkhn velkhe monat?

00:27:58.990 --> 00:28:00.300
in may.

00:27:59.682 --> 00:28:01.667
may, fir un fertsik.

00:28:01.420 --> 00:28:06.982
fir un fertsik. az ikh gleyb iz dos geven nokhn tsvontsikstn may beerekh.

00:28:09.233 --> 00:28:15.115
dort, dernokh dem, m'hot genumen di key- di kleyder oyskokhn,

00:28:17.080 --> 00:28:24.634
mikh hot men genumen, az ikh zol geyn aroysvarfn di kleyder vu m'hot es oysgekokht. vi lang ikh bin gekumen iz shoyn mayn bruder Avrom dort nisht gevezn.

00:28:24.707 --> 00:28:26.456
m'hot undz tserisn dortn.

00:28:27.019 --> 00:28:29.190
dort hot men yedern gegebn a numer,

00:28:29.820 --> 00:28:35.366
ikh hob gehat a numer, azoy vi a shtikl skhoyre, fun der linker zayt iz gevezn.

00:28:35.625 --> 00:28:40.260
a dray-UHOLNIK a geler, un oyf dem iz gevezn a BUKVA U.

00:28:40.283 --> 00:28:46.942
dos hot geheysn fun Ungvarn. un mayn heftling's numer iz gevezn finef un fuftsik toyznt nul nayn un akhtsik.

00:28:49.007 --> 00:28:52.831
un ze'mir gevezn dortn, dernokh dem, may-

00:28:51.471 --> 00:28:54.334
ir hot gekumen a numer, ober nisht,

00:28:53.125 --> 00:28:56.564
a numer, yo. nisht oyf der, oyf der oyf der linker zayt.

00:28:54.501 --> 00:28:56.115
nisht oyfn,

00:28:57.900 --> 00:29:01.120
ACHSHAV NATZOR VENAVOR LAKELET HABAAH.
